    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 6. Caballerocotyla llewelyni n. sp. 1. Holotype ventral view. 2. Anchors. 3. Ovary and terminal genitalia of paratype. 4. Light micrograph of total worm. 5. Light micrograph of egg with four filaments. 6. Confocal scanning light micrograph, haptor with papillae and marginal membrane. Scales­bars: 1, 1 mm; 2, 0.05 mm; 3, 0.5 mm." ;
